1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,500
Welcome to the Video Caption Generator tutorial.

2
00:00:03,500 --> 00:00:07,200
This application helps you create professional subtitles quickly and easily.

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:10,800
You can upload video files or record live speech for real-time transcription.

4
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:14,500
The speech recognition technology supports over 50 languages worldwide.

5
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:18,200
Simply click the upload button to select your video file from your computer.

6
00:00:18,200 --> 00:00:21,800
Supported formats include MP4, WebM, MOV, and AVI files.

7
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:25,400
For live recording, click the microphone button and speak clearly.

8
00:00:25,400 --> 00:00:29,100
The application will automatically convert your speech to text in real-time.

9
00:00:29,100 --> 00:00:32,800
You can edit the generated subtitles using the timeline editor below.

10
00:00:32,800 --> 00:00:36,500
Drag the subtitle blocks to adjust timing or click to edit the text content.

11
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:40,200
Translation features allow you to convert subtitles to different languages.

12
00:00:40,200 --> 00:00:43,900
Configure your Google Translate API key in settings for translation support.

13
00:00:43,900 --> 00:00:47,600
Customize the appearance with font size, color, and background options.

14
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:51,300
Export your subtitles in multiple formats including SRT, WebVTT, and ASS.

15
00:00:51,300 --> 00:00:55,000
You can also export videos with burned-in subtitles for final distribution.

16
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:58,700
The application works offline for basic features and includes dark mode support.

17
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,400
Keyboard shortcuts help speed up your workflow during editing sessions.

18
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:06,100
Press Space to play or pause, and use arrow keys to navigate the timeline.

19
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:09,800
The responsive design ensures the application works on both desktop and mobile devices.

20
00:01:09,800 --> 00:01:13,500
Thank you for using the Video Caption Generator. Happy subtitling!